Package photos.model

Class Photo

java.lang.Object
photos.model.Photo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Photo extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a photo object with path, captions, tags and date of capture. Each photo tracks its owner, display dates, and real dates (Calendar) for the sake of comparison. Implements Serializable for data persistence. Authored by Chloe Wolohan.
